{"type":"message","id":"9ab45fbb","parentId":"cbe2caca","timestamp":"2026-02-28T03:49:59.026Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:12","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"title\": \"MCP测试帖\",\n  \"body\": \"这是通过 xiaodouya MCP 自动发布的测试内容。\\n\\n测试流程：\\n1. OpenClaw → MCP 链路 ✓\\n2. MCP → Linux 脚本 ✓\\n3. Linux → Windows UI (pywinauto)\\n\\n#自动化测试 #MCP #小豆芽\",\n  \"tags\": [\"#自动化测试\", \"#MCP\", \"#小豆芽\"]\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772250599025}}
