{"type":"message","id":"c5cca91e","parentId":"a1bfa285","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:36:05.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我重新 review xiaodouya MCP，看看能不能开始测试发布帖子。让我先读取 XIAODOUYA_MCP_RUNBOOK_ZH.md 文件来了解当前状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先读取 runbook 文件，了解当前 MCP 的状态和下一步测试计划。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:73","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/XIAODOUYA_MCP_RUNBOOK_ZH.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":48805,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48944,"cost":{"input":0.0000048805,"output":2.78e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000049083}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772256948082}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff5aa4a3","parentId":"c5cca91e","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:36:05.447Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:73","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 小豆芽 MCP 配置与使用手册（OpenClaw / Linux-WSL 直控 Windows）\n\n## 1. 目标与架构\n\n- OpenClaw 运行在 Linux（WSL）。\n- 通过 MCP 工具调用 Linux 脚本。\n- Linux 脚本再通过 `powershell.exe` 调 Windows `python` + `pywinauto` 控制小豆芽。\n\n链路：\n`OpenClaw -> MCP(xiaodouya_mcp_server.py) -> controller.py -> Windows PowerShell -> pywinauto`\n\n## 2. 关键路径（当前环境）\n\n- 项目目录：`/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya`\n- MCP 配置：`/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/mcp.json`\n- OpenClaw 主配置：`/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- 证据目录（默认）：`/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/evidence`\n\n## 3. 先修复网关（必须）\n\n### 3.1 已知坑（本次断连根因）\n\n`openclaw.json` 里不能启用不存在的插件 `plugins.entries.mcp-integration`。  \n否则网关会反复失败，表现为：`ECONNREFUSED 127.0.0.1:18789`。\n\n### 3.2 正确做法\n\n- 保留 Feishu 插件配置。\n- **删除** `plugins.entries.mcp-integration`。\n- MCP 服务器统一放到 `~/.openclaw/mcp.json`，不要写到 `plugins.entries`。\n\n## 4. 配置 xiaodouya MCP\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/mcp.json`，确保包含：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"xiaodouya-linux-win-control\": {\n      \"command\": \"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/.venv-xiaodouya/bin/python\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/xiaodouya_mcp_server.py\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n如果已经有其他 MCP（如 playwright），只需把该条目合并进去，不要覆盖整个文件。\n\n## 5. 环境自检（Linux 侧）\n\n在 Linux 执行：\n\n```bash\n# 1) 网关状态\nopenclaw status --all\nopenclaw health --json\n\n# 2) 检查 mcp 配置\nsed -n 1,220p ~/.openclaw/mcp.json\n\n# 3) 检查项目文件\nls -la /home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya\n```\n\n预期：\n\n- `Gateway ... reachable`\n- `Feishu ... OK`\n- `mcp.json` 含 `xiaodouya-linux-win-control`\n\n## 6. 环境自检（Windows 侧，经 WSL 调用）\n\n在 Linux 执行：\n\n```bash\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/cmd.exe /c \"python --version\"\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/cmd.exe /c \"C:\\\\Users\\\\yuyirong\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\Python\\\\Python311\\\\python.exe -m pip show pywinauto\"\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/v1.0/powershell.exe -NoProfile -Command \"Test-Path C:\\Program Files\\xiaodouya\\新榜小豆芽.exe\"\n```\n\n如果 `python --version` 仍是商店占位符（提示 Python was not found），请用绝对路径调用 Python311，或补装 Python。\n\n## 7. 在 OpenClaw 中如何调用\n\n推荐顺序：\n\n1. `xdy_validate_selectors`：先验证 `selectors.yaml`。\n2. `xdy_run_workflow`：跑主流程（默认 `mode=prepublish`）。\n3. `xdy_get_status`：查看 run 状态。\n4. 失败时用 `xdy_resume` 或 `xdy_step` 定点重试。\n\n### 7.1 建议提示词（给 OpenClaw）\n\n```text\n先调用 xdy_validate_selectors。\n如果通过，则调用 xdy_run_workflow：\n- content_file=/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/content_example.json\n- mode=prepublish\n执行后再调用 xdy_get_status 返回 run_id 的结果。\n```\n\n### 7.2 生产安全建议\n\n- 默认只用 `prepublish`，停在发布前人工确认。\n- 只有明确需要自动发布时，才用 `mode=publish`。\n\n## 8. 常见问题与处理\n\n### 8.1 Gateway 断开 / ECONNREFUSED\n\n- 先查：`openclaw status --all`\n- 若看到配置错误，检查 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 是否误加了 `mcp-integration`。\n- 修复后重启：\n\n```bash\nsystemctl --user restart openclaw-gateway\n```\n\n### 8.2 `windows python not found in PATH: python.exe`\n\n- 这是 Windows Python 未安装或 PATH 仅有商店别名。\n- 用绝对路径：\n  `C:\\Users\\yuyirong\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python311\\python.exe`\n- 并安装依赖：\n\n```bash\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/cmd.exe /c \"C:\\\\Users\\\\yuyirong\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\Python\\\\Python311\\\\python.exe -m pip install -U pip pywinauto pyyaml\"\n```\n\n### 8.3 小豆芽路径不一致\n\n当前控制器默认：\n`C:\\Program Files\\xiaodouya\\新榜小豆芽.exe`\n\n若你机器实际路径不同，修改：\n`/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/controller.py` 中 `DEFAULT_APP_PATH`。\n\n### 8.4 睡眠后断联\n\n- WSL / SSH 链路会受主机睡眠影响。\n- 关键调试阶段建议关闭自动睡眠，保证长任务不断线。\n\n## 9. 一键排查命令（复制即用）\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status --all && \\\nopenclaw health --json && \\\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/cmd.exe /c \"python --version\" && \\\n/mnt/c/Windows/System32/cmd.exe /c \"if exist C:\\\\Users\\\\yuyirong\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\Python\\\\Python311\\\\python.exe (echo HAS_PY311) else (echo NO_PY311)\"\n```\n\n---\n\n如需恢复错误配置，先备份当前文件再改：\n\n```bash\ncp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772256965444}}
